  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à D-Bus GLib</title>

    <para>
      The <application>D-Bus GLib</application> package contains
      <application>GLib</application> interfaces to the
      <application>D-Bus</application> API.
    </para>

    &lfs73_checked;

